Castle Fantasia Renewal 2
Company: Studio e.go!
Release date: Dec 22, 2000
Genre: Strategy JRPG/ Visual Novel


Summary: The 200 year long war between Lushiera and Injiera continues. This is the story of a hero who changes the course of this neverending war and the lives of people around him. In Castle Fantasia 2 you play as Hewie, commander of the seventh holy knight corps. He has a keen mind for strategy and tactics, seeing through and predicting enemy plans. However, his laid-back attitude causes him to be kept in a low regard by his commanding officers, friends and even his subordinates.


Translator: BTAxis 


